text: Milenko Lekić (born 5 April 1936) is a Serbian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Subotica
